    • Constructor Detail

      • Exam

        public Exam​(Course course,
            Class theClass,
            Room examRoom,
            boolean isWritten)
        Four-argument constructor.Initializes variables and sets the hour and minute of an Exam to 8:30 by default. The teacher for the exam is set by getting the course's assigned teacher. A new ArrayList of dates is also created to be able to make exams that last several days.
        Parameters:
        course - a Course object
        theClass - a Class object
        examRoom - a Room object
        isWritten - determines if the exam is written
